=== Growth Considerations

Severe illness during adolescence can affect growth. Monitoring:

    - *Height and weight*: Track on growth curves at each medical contact
    - *Nutritional status*: Ensure adequate calories and protein despite reduced appetite
    - *Pubertal development*: Chronic illness can delay puberty; document Tanner staging
    - *Growth velocity*: Slowing growth velocity may warrant endocrine evaluation

